{"tid":1785273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逾半首投族fb收政治資訊 網紅影響大","createTime":"2019-12-16T09:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T09:10:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5876acf8f880e67b779848e54d9d4603c67547f7","tid":1785273,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:08:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191216/N43C3DBBROJE5M7FJR43RQTYA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191216%2FN43C3DBBROJE5M7FJR43RQTYA4%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7pggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=249c93a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191216%2FN43C3DBBROJE5M7FJR43RQTYA4%2F&h=545ef70e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191216/N43C3DBBROJE5M7FJR43RQTYA4/</a><br />\n<br />\n逾半首投族fb收政治資訊 網紅影響大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/axIvZ3HhPDvvUC-MIxEyPCOJAlo=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/JFF2TNRUBTCPUP3IDSVQDVPX2M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FaxIvZ3HhPDvvUC-MIxEyPCOJAlo%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FJFF2TNRUBTCPUP3IDSVQDVPX2M.gif&h=f8ae35d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡英文昨日在彰化助選時，引臂呼籲選民繼續支持她。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】台灣財經雜誌《商業周刊》上月有關台首投族的問卷調查顯示，首投世代接受政治資訊的來源，透過fb等社交平台達50.8%，YouTuber與網紅佔8.1%，甚至比家人的影響還高。相信這也是總統蔡英文不惜放下身段，與網紅一同亮相原因。<br />\n<br />\n台灣師範大學政治所教授范世平認為，選舉關鍵在於年輕人是否願意投票，2016年選前發生韓國女團TWICE的台灣成員周子瑜「國旗」風波，激發年輕人投票給蔡，但今屆選舉沒突發事件的話，年輕選民投票意欲未必太高。<br />\n<br />\n范世平教授稱，蔡英文的民調遙遙領先主要對手韓國瑜，從民進黨或蔡英文的文宣可見，競選團隊已將韓國瑜邊緣化，重點放在立委席次，只要議席過半就能繼續完全執政。他又稱，每屆總統選舉實際投票約1,300萬人，首投族約118萬人，加上年老選民去世，至少200萬選票在新一屆選舉中出現變動，影響選舉結果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n年輕選民投票意欲未必高<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：民進黨轟國民黨「一國兩制幫兇」<br />\n<br />\n台灣制憲基金會執行長林宜正早前分析，蔡英文要用選票力抗中共滲透，以投票率七成估算，蔡須獲六成以上、812萬選票，比2016年的689萬票多出兩成青年票，目標就能夠達成。<br />\n<br />\n不過，范教授認為，周子瑜事件（周子瑜2016年參加韓國綜藝節目持青天白日滿地紅旗，被過氣歌手黃安指撐台獨，周被迫拍短片道歉）激發年輕人投票給蔡，但今屆選舉沒有突發事件的話，加上學校期末考，未必能引起年輕選民投票意欲。"},{"pid":"84edd53ee39c7b3579c6d0c4838427573bade798","tid":1785273,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnDkzda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnDkzda.jpg&h=97bc3868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY03AQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPY03AQa.jpg&h=511bc04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=f485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a&amp;oe=5EAED219\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3Df485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a%26oe%3D5EAED219&h=70a59658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79361407_152866279456715_1551513620934819840_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_oc=AQmAvyxgZu5T2VDaPtTOxDhzelZTE0Kn6aEMZ7R4p1do2OXZP_vbNkrmi7bn7Ml2AHk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=703c1ff8ccb8fc8cc77d959ea38cd7d7&amp;oe=5EB36A76\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79361407_152866279456715_1551513620934819840_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_oc%3DAQmAvyxgZu5T2VDaPtTOxDhzelZTE0Kn6aEMZ7R4p1do2OXZP_vbNkrmi7bn7Ml2AHk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3D703c1ff8ccb8fc8cc77d959ea38cd7d7%26oe%3D5EB36A76&h=ca3dd940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b4c7709b41b5460c869200977463aae34267a87","tid":1785273,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:10:08.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}